snippet.title: The Purple Coin Gameplay (Fan Game)
snippet.description: Take a look at http://mfgg.net/ for more awesome Mario themed fan games! Hey, another fun thing to do while watching this video and you're a Mario 64 Machinimist is try to find your own Color Code, i saw several ones which reminded me of someone. More fan games and machinima's coming soon!
